    "discount_panel_heading": "WHY OUR PRICES WORKS DIFFERENTLY",
    "discount_panel_content": "<p>Great art doesn’t just fill a wall - it shapes a space, sets a mood, and tells a story that’s uniquely yours.</p><p>This is your chance to build something more intentional. To curate, combine, and create a home that feels considered down to the last detail.</p><p><strong>Buy 2 get 1 free</strong> or <strong>Buy 3 get 2 free</strong></p><p>By choosing multiple pieces in one order, you’re not only expanding your collection - you’re also reducing packaging, cutting down on shipments, and making a more conscious choice without compromising on style.</p><p>Bring cohesion to a room. Mix contrasts. Create moments that feel personal.</p><p></p><p><em>Thoughtful idea:</em> </p><p>Keep your favorites and set the rest aside as meaningful gifts - pieces that feel just as curated as the spaces they’ll end up in.</p><p>Because collecting art should feel effortless, intentional, and a little bit generous.</p><p><strong>More pieces. More personality. Smarter choices.</strong></p>",
    "vendor_panel_content": "<p>Art for Causes - offers three distinct release categories all connected to a good cause.</p>",
    "price_panel_heading": "THE IDEA BEHIND THE PRICE",
    "price_panel_content": "<p>Nothing here is random.</p><p>Every decision - from how pieces are released to how they’re offered - is built around doing more with less. Less excess, fewer unnecessary steps, and a sharper focus on what actually creates value.</p><p>That’s what makes these prices possible.</p><p>Not shortcuts. Not compromises.<br/>Just a system designed to be more efficient, more thoughtful, and ultimately more fair.</p><p>It means you get access to more, while the overall footprint stays smaller.</p><p>And it means every piece you choose carries a bit more intention - not just in how it looks, but in how it exists.</p><p>No noise. No overproduction. No inflated layers.</p><p>Just a smarter way of doing things.</p><p><strong>Less excess. More meaning.</strong></p>",
